# Set default behaviors to automatically normalize line endings.
# ===========================================================================
# Handle line endings automatically for files detected as text
# and leave all files detected as binary untouched.
# This will handle all files NOT explicitly defined below.

# Hybrid: This will check in as LF, but checkout matching the OS.
* text=auto
# Force NATIVE line-endings. (ie: crlf on Windows, lf on Linux, etc.)
# * text
# Explicitly declare all files to always have specific line-endings.
# * text eol=lf

# Force CRLF line-endings.
*.bat      eol=crlf
*.BAT      eol=crlf
*.cmd      eol=crlf
*.CMD      eol=crlf
